{"tid":2431052,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有1/3至1/2已預約的人無到場接種科興疫苗，中心強調靠市民自行判斷是否適合注射","createTime":"2021-03-03T11:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T11:45:07.000Z","uid":350584,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cabd0bebe5f1c7bbbb8e37565697409293619d5f","tid":2431052,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:05:13.000Z","msg":"不少市民今日繼續到社區疫苗接種中心接種科興疫苗。亦有部分市民「打退堂鼓」，無按預約時間到場，亦有人查詢後後決定不接種。有接種中心負責人近中午時表示，有三分一至一半已預約的人無到場，又強調要靠市民自行判斷，是否適合注射疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n政府專家顧問許樹昌說，有市民接種疫苗後死亡，估計很大機會與本身的心血管疾病有關，暫時不會剎停接種計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578555-20210303.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578555-20210303.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiXwEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=b5bfa137\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578555-20210303.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=74ae4c25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578555-20210303.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"012afc6741e0cb73986a9a39f90e905b022e8505","tid":2431052,"uid":350584,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:06:17.000Z","msg":"政府專家顧問許樹昌說，有市民接種疫苗後死亡，估計很大機會與本身的心血管疾病有關，暫時不會剎停接種計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ef2ba559711c61c41aa16638bd12c7d6e718d9","tid":2431052,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:07:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ioHUx5q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FioHUx5q.jpg&h=80f2aa4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n疫苗出門恕不負責"},{"pid":"057fa8e495378a39af393d37e1c8b820356670fe","tid":2431052,"uid":8420,